2002;;Night at the Golden Eagle;;American;;Adam Rifkin;;Donnie Mantemarano, Vinny Argiro, Natasha Lyonne;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Night_at_the_Golden_Eagle;;Two elderly criminals spend their final night in Los Angeles, California at the Golden Eagle Hotel prior to their departure to Las Vegas, Nevada, to lead a life without crime. Unfortunately, on the hottest night of the summer, these two ex-criminals seemingly get caught in the malice of prostitutes, pimps, drunken bums, fighting monkeys, and young runaways.